F</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614175\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3614175\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kno1665702715076.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kno1665702715076.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kno1665702715076.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kno1665702715076\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Caption </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values:\n         <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715076__section_w1130ab1b5b1_w1131ab1b5_w1132ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1__entry__2\"> Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1__entry__2\">The form is displayed with a title bar. If a\n                        value is provided for the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Title</span> form property, this\n                        value is displayed in the title bar. Otherwise, the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Name</span> is displayed. Default if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window\n                           Type</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Normal</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">Primary</code>,\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">Secondary</code>, or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Dialog</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10961e1_d10962e1_d10963e1__entry__2\">No title bar is displayed, and the\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">System Menu</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Iconize</span>,\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Maximize</span>, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span>\n                        properties are also disabled. Default if <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span>\n                        is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Contained</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">Popup</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715076__section_xzd_ydl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1006380e159\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"kno1665702715076__table_d10964e1_d10965e1_d10966e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Window Type</span>, <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Iconize</span>,\n                           <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Maximize</span>, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715076__section_jj4_c2l_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1006380e208\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kno1665702715076__p_d97469e1_d97470e1_d97471e1\">When a form is activated as a popup window, the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caption</span> property is not applied. If the form is instantiated\n            with <code class=\"ph codeph\"> InheritWinProps=True</code>, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caption</span> property\n            is applied only if it has been explicitly set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kno1665702715076__section_x5p_k2l_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1006380e229\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"kno1665702715076__ul_x5g_m2l_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kno1665702715076__li_d39578e1_d39579e1_d39580e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kno1665702715076__li_d39581e1_d39582e1_d39583e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1705472567076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1705472567076.html\" title=\"An application shell is the first object that is executed when a Windows or character mode application is started. It determines how the application is initialized and the first form component that is displayed.\">Application Shells for Desktop Applications</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1665702689407.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Title</a><p>Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Name</a><p>Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>System Menu (SysMenu)</a><p>Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cwr1665702715216.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Iconize (CanIconize)</a><p>Window property that determines whether the user can minimize the form or application window at run time, and enables the Minimize/Restore button in the title bar.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qkn1665702715286.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Maximize</a><p>Determines whether the user can maximize and restore the size of the form or application window using the Maximize/Restore button in the title bar.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ugr1665702834531.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Close (CanClose) [FRM]</a><p>Window property of a form component that determines whether the user can close the form window by clicking the Close button in the title bar.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614175\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614175\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Caption Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Caption Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False . Value Description True The form is displayed with a title bar. If a value is provided for the Title form property, this value is displayed in the title bar. Otherwise, the Name is displayed. Default if Window Type is Normal , Primary , Secondary , or Dialog . False No title bar is displayed, and the System Menu , Iconize , Maximize , and Close properties are also disabled. Default if Window Type is Contained or Popup . Usage Dynamic? No Dependencies: Window Type , Iconize , Maximize , and Close Description When a form is activated as a popup window, the Caption property is not applied. If the form is instantiated with InheritWinProps=True , the Caption property is applied only if it has been explicitly set to true . Applies To Form Application Shells for Desktop Applications Related Links Title Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed. Name Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it. System Menu (SysMenu) Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False. Iconize (CanIconize) Window property that determines whether the user can minimize the form or application window at run time, and enables the Minimize/Restore button in the title bar. Maximize Determines whether the user can maximize and restore the size of the form or application window using the Maximize/Restore button in the title bar. Close (CanClose) [FRM] Window property of a form component that determines whether the user can close the form window by clicking the Close button in the title bar. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}